# usage:

# on a control machine:
# - store the contents of this file in /etc/ansible/hosts
# - store an ssh key authorized for managed nodes in ~/.ssh
# - (optionally): specify Host/HostName/User/IdentityFile in ~/.ssh/config

# on a managed node:
# - add an ssh key from the control machine to the `authorized_keys` of the managed node
# - (optionally): add your user and give it sudo privs on the node

